| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0734 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6bac907b-82e7-5725-b67b-f64bcbe9bd63"
